tivation<\\/strong> is difficult to change. Don\'t focus on it. Rewards are great but not effective <strong>unless they perform the behavior first.<\\/strong>\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"39\":\"\",\"23\":\"Reaserch & Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>My design goal is to gather a thriving global profession of best-in-class customer cares experts across all industries, and LP also influences the community by sharing knowledge and provides trainings as industry lead; Builds up a member-driven organization committed to promoting customer care and customer engagement as a competitive advantage in business; This website can be a soft sale tool that Introduce LP\'s 2.0 platform, mobile applications and its benefits.<\\/p><p>I led the website UX design for ACCPI commnity site. The goal is to reshape the LivePerson\'s (LP) brand\\u2019s online presence, through creating a sleek sharable community experiences and transferring the site focus to nurturing a customer care professional which would offer more engaging online experiences for customers. As a IA and UX person, I conducted researches and came up with a series of ideations before planning and restructuring the site, followed by important considerations from both design and development point of view. Here is a work in progress for ACCPI website.\\r\\n<\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Research & analysis<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>IA & sitemap<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Persona<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Use flow<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Wireframes<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Interactive prototype<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Testing<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"LivePerson\",\"11\":\"http:\\/\\/www.liveperson.com\\/\",\"58\":\"yellow\",\"25\":{\"185\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Persona\",\"body\":\"<p>In order to demostrate our target audience for ACCPI, I\'ve created 5 personas, here list two as examples. Their working experience level as a customer care professional is about junior to mid-weight. Full persona list and analysis will be provided by request.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"182\",\"183\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"189\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"User Flow\",\"body\":\"<p>Back to my analysis before, I think the community will be relatively open unless visitor wants to take action. The trigger can be the game, the social press of our community but most important, the ACCPI website content itself.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"188\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"187\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Sitemap\",\"body\":\"<p>Back to my analysis before, I think the community will be relatively open unless visitor wants to take action. The trigger can be the game, the social press of our community but most important, the ACCPI website content itself.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"186\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"191\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Wireframes\",\"body\":\"<p>Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"192\",\"193\",\"194\"],\"layout\":\"fluid\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"new1\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Polished Design\",\"body\":\"<p>Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"195\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Design\",\"14\":\"ACCPI\\r\\nCommunity Website\",\"22\":\"<p>I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan. To coincide with the a series of the campaign, our team was under extreme pressure to move fast. We were tasked to deliver from ideation to high\\u2010fidelity prototype to our technical production partner within 4 weeks, so it requires quick turnarounds. The combination of a fixed deadline, content strategy, usability testing, and usability testing meant I needed to get the experience right in the first two weeks.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"18\"],\"17\":\" I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan.\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\":\"ACCPI Community Website\",\"13\":[\"7\"],\"42\":[\"17\"],\"50\":\"https:\\/\\/accpi.org\\/\",\"44\":[\"16\"],\"12\":\"Researches, Wireframes, UX Design & Testing\",\"3\":\" I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan.\",\"9\":[\"photoshop\",\"axure\",\"sketch\"],\"4\":\"2015\"}}', '2015-08-25 05:15:33', '2015-08-25 05:15:33', '7460c67e-ab5d-4f1c-9ba9-1bb047269a91');
