46-32bc-4383-9116-07c0279e3625'),
 ('322', '10', '3', '1', 'en_us', '36', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"LivePerson Website\",\"slug\":\"liveperson-website\",\"postDate\":1430364600,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"24\":\"<p>This is the analysis text.\\r\\n<\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>The page doesn\'t impress me, as a first-time visitor after seeing a few slides in the header image area. It simply was not able to convey what it is.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>The look and feel of the overall layout didn\'t match its content. The logo could also be redesigned to be more coherent to a writer\'s community.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>There is no quick upload functionality for sharing your work and the sign up process is too long.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Kanjy allows writers to create portfolios of their work, but it\'s still not sufficient to make the whole community an active network.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"39\":\"\",\"23\":\"Analysis Heading\",\"20\":\"<p>I led the website UX design for LivePerson global where I worked. The goal I set is to reshape the brand\\u2019s online presence, through creating a sleek user interface and transferring the site focus to B2C which would offer more engaging online experiences for customers.<\\/p><p>As a IA and UX person, I conducted researches and came up with a series of ideations before planning and restructuring the site, followed by some important considerations from both design and development point of view.<\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"LivePerson\",\"11\":\"http:\\/\\/www.liveperson.com\\/\",\"58\":\"yellow\",\"25\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Original Pricing Model\",\"body\":\"<p>After changing from the old plan, the same issues are still relevant with the new pricing model and sale strategy:\\r\\n<\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Visitors want to see pricings and features in the same table;<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Visitors want to understand the differences between plans and goals;<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Visitors do not understand the buzz words (which do not sound like buzz words);<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul><p>A test on a mobile user, who has some frustrations when using it.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"218\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"146\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Design - Wireframes\",\"body\":\"<p>Based on the above data and user analysis, I think the key point for the new pricing page should be:\\r\\n<\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li>Focus on Pricing itself instead of explain un unfamiliar concept for visitors(especially as we are using a new pricing model and drive traffic, there will be more first-time-visitor.)<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Clearly present what we sell to visitors: it is a combo of partially functional mobile app and a web dashboard, so what users finally get will meet their expectation.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\\"Why should I pay if you have a free plan?\\\" will be the No1 question visitor will ask if he\\/ she see our pricing page; emphasize the free plan but also compare it with our other plan.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Target visitors better by supplying related testimonial and Q&As (also valuable for future analysis and improvement.)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"media\":[\"144\",\"145\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"149\":{\"type\":\"comparisonFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Design - Wireframes\",\"body\":\"<p>Based on the above data and user analysis, I think the key point for the new pricing page should be:<\\/p><ul><li>Focus on Pricing itself instead of explain un unfamiliar concept for visitors(especially as we are using a new pricing model and drive traffic, there will be more first-time-visitor.)<\\/li><li>Clearly present what we sell to visitors: it is a combo of partially functional mobile app and a web dashboard, so what users finally get will meet their expectation.<\\/li><li>\\\"Why should I pay if you have a free plan?\\\" will be the No1 question visitor will ask if he\\/ she see our pricing page; emphasize the free plan but also compare it with our other plan.<\\/li><li>Target visitors better by supplying related testimonial and Q&As (also valuable for future analysis and improvement.)<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"images\":[\"147\",\"148\"],\"firstCaption\":\"Plan A\",\"secondCaption\":\"Plan B\",\"fadeEnabled\":\"1\"}},\"19\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Other works at\\r\\nLivePerson\",\"body\":\"<p>Details are available upon request.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"141\",\"142\"],\"layout\":\"fluid\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"65\":{\"type\":\"responsiveFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Responsive Design\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the text content for responsive design feature. This is the text content for responsive design feature. This is the text content for responsive design feature. This is the text content for responsive design feature.<\\/p>\",\"desktopScreen\":[\"67\"],\"tabletScreen\":[\"66\"],\"mobileScreen\":[\"64\"],\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Design\",\"14\":\"LivePerson\\r\\nWebsite\",\"22\":\"<p>I\'ve learned a lot.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"133\"],\"17\":\"\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\":\"\",\"13\":[\"7\"],\"42\":[\"111\"],\"50\":\"\",\"44\":[\"95\"],\"12\":\"Visual Design\",\"3\":\"I led the UX design for LivePerson where I worked. My goal is to reshape the brand\\u2019s online presence by creating a sleek user interface and transferring the focus to B2C.\",\"9\":[\"photoshop\"],\"4\":\"2014\"}}', '2015-08-27 01:22:28', '2015-08-27 01:22:28', 'cc8ce0ab-b3c9-43a8-8ef0-9daa838f8db2'),
