 ('362', '262', '3', '1', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Candidates Tracking System\",\"slug\":\"candidates-tracking-system\",\"postDate\":1440736140,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"24\":\"<p>According to an article in HR resource ERE.net, one of the biggest struggles recruiters are starting to encounter is the need to make a quick hire. Many HR professionals had time during the recession to deliberate over candidates\' qualifications and conduct multiple rounds of interviews, but competition is heating up once more for great talent. In addition, many companies are growing so fast and need to fill multiple positions at the same time that recruiters no longer have a lot of time to recruit workers.<\\/p>\",\"39\":\"\",\"23\":\"Project Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>According to an article in HR resource ERE.net, one of the biggest struggles recruiters are starting to encounter is the need to make a quick hire. Many HR professionals had time during the recession to deliberate over candidates\' qualifications and conduct multiple rounds of interviews, but competition is heating up once more for great talent. In addition, many companies are growing so fast and need to fill multiple positions at the same time that recruiters no longer have a lot of time to recruit workers.<\\/p><p>Also, HR professionals often see themselves stuck when they aren\'t receiving resumes from candidates with strong backgrounds or skill sets needed for the position. Even if these recruiters reach out to passive job seekers, they may hit a brick wall in terms of finding the talent they need. This is an all-too-common problem for recruiters, but one that they are starting to face more often as the competition for key performers heats up.<\\/p><p>As for Interviewer, it is hard for them to make sure the new hires need to be able to integrate into a team and work well in the company environment- after all, reading candidate\'s drive is part of HR\'s skill. So how can they work together seamless?<\\/p><p>Moreover, miscommunication, delayed updating interview schedules always slow down the process. The interview room always the first place an interviewer see an candidates\' resume. Then how can they make the professional skill based judgement in 20 mins?<\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"\",\"11\":\"\",\"58\":\"blue\",\"25\":{\"265\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"An Embarrassing Conversation\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>Front Desk: <\\/strong>Hey Joe, your interviewee is waiting for you, are you ready?<\\/p><p><strong>Joe: <\\/strong>An interviewee? Never heard about it. Are we hiring?<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"264\"],\"layout\":\"fluid\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"263\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Personas\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"260\",\"261\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"267\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Ideations\",\"body\":\"<ul><li>Intuitive candidate based tracking flow and manageable pipeline.<\\/li><li>Administrator login and visitor login funnel. Team tools for sharing, scheduling and feedback collection.<\\/li><li>Seamless integrate with Gmail, Outlook and Calendar.<\\/li><li>Automatic resume parser but also accessible to original files.<\\/li><li>Recruiting intelligence, highlight candidates in keywords and descriptions.<\\/li><li>Scientific rating and weighting system help you avoid bias.<\\/li><li>Powerful search and filter function available.<\\/li><li>Connect with mainstream job pos