such as college students, or young couples who have an interest in building their living environment. Also including those who has an interest in online learning.<\\/p>\",\"39\":{\"56\":{\"type\":\"step\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"99\"]}},\"55\":{\"type\":\"step\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"98\"]}}},\"23\":\"Subject Research & Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>The Real-time Experience is an interactive 3D design project that\\r\\nintroduces daily feng shui tips to college students, office workers, and anyone who wants to learn\\r\\nhow feng shui can enhance their lives. This project uses Web GL technology that runs on any\\r\\ncomputer with an up-to-date, modern browser.\\r\\n<\\/p><p>The user flow is a simple four-step process: \\u201clisten,\\u201d \\u201cobserve,\\u201d \\u201cfind,\\u201d and \\u201csolve.\\u201d This is how\\r\\nfeng shui masters help people figure out their problems. It is an engaging practice because\\r\\nusers become actively involved in the whole problem-solving experience. My goal for this\\r\\nproject is to present the principles and rules of feng shui philosophy, as well as its applications\\r\\nin modern interior design and to interpret feng shui through creative interactive experience. I\\r\\nwish that by introducing feng shui to new western audience, they can benefit from learning\\r\\nfeng shui theories and improve their living environment. <\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"\",\"11\":\"\",\"58\":\"blue\",\"25\":{\"21\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Ideation \",\"body\":\"<p>Then I have an idea, instead of thinking how to covert new visitors to this topic, I\'d like to explore how feng shui theory can actually retain audience and what makes those audience addicted, so my next step is to discover the secrets of feng shui master. After watching videos, look up books and even attend several seminars by myself, I realized the people who really find feng shu helps thei