ur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"180\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"User Testing\",\"body\":\"<p>In order to better understand Hsin-Lei\'s music, we met at Beijing in early 2014. Hsin Lei inspired by Asian culture and transform into western style melody. This great conversation we had given me some new perspective to Hsin Lei and her music and the more I understand about her life, the more we can understand her music.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"172\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Application\",\"14\":\"Composer\\r\\nHsin-Lei Chen\\r\\nPortfolio\",\"22\":\"<p>A good design for a musical portfolio is not just playing some lovely tunes. It expresses the deepest feelings and emotions of the composer. Following with this direction, a multi-media form of experience can resonate with the audience.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"131\"],\"17\":\"This is the OG description.\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\":\"Composer Hsin-Lei Chen Portfolio\",\"13\":[\"7\"],\"42\":[\"112\"],\"50\":\"http:\\/\\/hsinlei.com\",\"44\":[\"70\"],\"12\":\"Visual Design, User Experience Design\",\"3\":\"An online listening experience and artist\'s archive for Hsin-Lei Chen, a Taiwanese composer who is known for her experimental folk music.\",\"9\":[\"photoshop\",\"css3\",\"html5\",\"javascript\",\"sketch\",\"webgl\"],\"4\":\"2015\"}}', '2015-11-06 02:06:52', '2015-11-06 02:06:52', 'a86fc881-721c-4aa6-ac22-e66d6d93f1ca'),
 ('490', '12', '3', '1', 'en_us', '51', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Composer Hsin-Lei Chen Portfolio\",\"slug\":\"hsin-lei\",\"postDate\":1430877900,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"24\":\"<p>This is the project analysis text.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"39\":{\"156\":{\"type\":\"step\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"155\"]}}},\"23\":\"Project Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>I\'ve got a chance to make a portfolio website for Hsin-Lei: a friend of mine, and a talented classical\\/experimental music composer.<\\/p><p>To fully understand Hsin-Lei\'s music before determining the art direction, we kept discussing about her musical pieces and exchanging my design blueprints with her feedbacks. I found her styles were heavily influenced by the European masters of classical music. Grown up and rooted in Chinese culture, most of her songs are also relevant to traditional Chinese literature and philosophies, flavored her work with some unique Asian tastes. Those conversations inspired me of a multimedia website, which represents the essential spirits of her work, using a calm color palette and some stylish photography.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"Hsin-Lei Chen\",\"11\":\"http:\\/\\/hsinlei.com\",\"58\":\"blue\",\"25\":{\"138\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a\\r\\ndesktop feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts. This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"137\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"desktop\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"103\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"136\",\"134\",\"135\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"181\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Interface Design\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"180\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"User Testing\",\"body\":\"<p>In order to better understand Hsin-Lei\'s music, we met at Beijing in early 2014. Hsin Lei inspired by Asian culture and transform into western style melody. This great conversation we had given me some new perspective to Hsin Lei and her music and the more I understand about her life, the more we can understand her music.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"172\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Application\",\"14\":\"Composer\\r\\nHsin-Lei Chen\\r\\nPortfolio\",\"22\":\"<p>A good design for a musical portfolio is not just playing some lovely tunes. It expresses the deepest feelings and emotions of the composer. Following with this direction, a multi-media form of experience can resonate with the audience.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"131\"],\"17\":\"This is the OG description.\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\":\"Composer Hsin-Lei Chen Portfolio\",\"13\":[\"7\"],\"42\":[\"112\"],\"50\":\"http:\\/\\/hsinlei.com\",\"44\":[\"70\"],\"12\":\"Visual Design, User Experience Design\",\"3\":\"An online listening experience and artist\'s archive for Hsin-Lei Chen, a Taiwanese composer who is known for her experimental folk music.\",\"9\":[\"photoshop\",\"css3\",\"html5\",\"javascript\",\"sketch\",\"webgl\"],\"4\":\"2015\"}}', '2015-11-06 02:43:27', '2015-11-06 02:43:27', '4430a84d-3298-44fc-8a55-0b3d3953b0a1'),
 ('491', '12', '3', '1', 'en_us', '52', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Composer Hsin-Lei Chen Portfolio\",\"slug\":\"hsin-lei\",\"postDate\":1430877900,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"24\":\"<p>Usually, when a musician needs to create a portfolio, commonly known as a press kit, to demonstrate his or her musical background and work history. The portfolio showcases what Hsin Lei can offer, such as the her interests, genre, style and achievements. Portfolios are works in progress and evolve along with he or her career. So the portfolio should also have a CMS to make sure consistently updated can be made easily by Hsin Lei herself - to accurately represent her music and image. The steps to create a portfolio involve assessing her career path, organizing and arranging her work and choosing a format for its presentation.Here are some ideas I have in mind that can help Hsin Lei review her talent and makes this portfolio site a more sharable, unique spot.\\r\\n<\\/p><p><br>\\r\\n<\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><strong>Photography<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\tHer portfolio should contain a neat head-shot and needs to represent the image you want to convey. Since Hsin Lei is an independent composer, I suggested a close shot to fill the frame as much as possible. An bonus finding during our conversation is, Hsin Lei is a visual person- through her study, travel and field researches, she inspired by surrounding and keep notes by took photos and many of her music reflects those image resources and her abstract sketches.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<strong>Cover Letter and Bio<\\/strong> Since Hsin Lei only had a press blog before, for content strategy and SEO purpose, a bio and personal statement  including the style of her music and what Hsin Lei hope to accomplish with it will help her uncover many of the prospect of her and her music. Adding some personal touch will be also a good way to define herself as a professional and confident musician, such as when she released her first album or a hobby that has helped you shape your particular style of music.\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<strong>Demo <\\/strong>Put together a demonstration CD using songs that best represent her music and image. Since this is a self host site in the future, the number of songs to include depends on how many Hsin Lei is willing to share. So the site should be adaptable form a few tracks to a full-length album. If not specified, a good rule of thumb is to include no more than three or four songs. Assume the listener is a busy person and place your best foot forward, as you want to capture the listener\'s attention immediately.\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<strong>Press Clippings<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\tSave some pages\\/spaces including press clippings such as feature articles about her music. If she previously released an album, include good reviews and quotes about it. If she have a variety of clippings of different formats, such as features and reviews, dedicate them to specific pages rather than a random layout. For instance, provide headings to let the reader know he or she is looking at album reviews, features, interviews, quotes, etc.<span><\\/span>\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\"39\":{\"156\":{\"type\":\"step\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"155\"]}}},\"23\":\"Project Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>I\'ve got a chance to make a portfolio website for Hsin-Lei: a friend of mine, and a talented classical\\/experimental music composer.<\\/p><p>To fully understand Hsin-Lei\'s music before determining the art direction, we kept discussing about her musical pieces and exchanging my design blueprints with her feedbacks. I found her styles were heavily influenced by the European masters of classical music. Grown up and rooted in Chinese culture, most of her songs are also relevant to traditional Chinese literature and philosophies, flavored her work with some unique Asian tastes. Those conversations inspired me of a multimedia website, which represents the essential spirits of her work, using a calm color palette and some stylish photography.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"Hsin-Lei Chen\",\"11\":\"http:\\/\\/hsinlei.com\",\"58\":\"blue\",\"25\":{\"138\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a\\r\\ndesktop feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts. This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"137\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"desktop\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"103\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"136\",\"134\",\"135\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"181\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Interface Design\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"180\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"User Testing\",\"body\":\"<p>In order to better understand Hsin-Lei\'s music, we met at Beijing in early 2014. Hsin Lei inspired by Asian culture and transform into western style melody. This great conversation we had given me some new perspective to Hsin Lei and her music and the more I understand about her life, the more we can understand her music.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"172\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Application\",\"14\":\"Composer\\r\\nHsin-Lei Chen\\r\\nPortfolio\",\"22\":\"<p>A good design for a musical portfolio is not just playing some lovely tunes. It expresses the deepest feelings and emotions of the composer. Following with this direction, a multi-media form of experience can resonate with the audience.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"131\"],\"17\":\"This is the OG description.\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\":\"Composer Hsin-Lei Chen Portfolio\",\"13\":[\"7\"],\"42\":[\"112\"],\"50\":\"http:\\/\\/hsinlei.com\",\"44\":[\"70\"],\"12\":\"Visual Design, User Experience Design\",\"3\":\"An online listening experience and artist\'s archive for Hsin-Lei Chen, a Taiwanese composer who is known for her experimental folk music.\",\"9\":[\"photoshop\",\"css3\",\"html5\",\"javascript\",\"sketch\",\"webgl\"],\"4\":\"2015\"}}', '2015-11-06 02:49:01', '2015-11-06 02:49:01', '0e26df53-c85f-462c-96e6-2527c83ea99a'),
 ('492', '12', '3', '1', 'en_us', '53', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Composer Hsin-Lei Chen Portfolio\",\"slug\":\"hsin-lei\",\"postDate\":1430877900,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"24\":\"<p>I want Hsin-Lei\'s portfolio to archive her music background and career history, as a press kit. The steps to create a portfolio involve documenting her career path, arranging her work based on that and choosing a proper presentation form. Here are some ideas to expose her talents through making this portfolio a unique spot on the Internet, and shareable.<\\/p><p><br>\\r\\n<\\/p><ul>\\r\\n\\t<li><strong>Photography<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\tHer portfolio should display a artistic portrait representing the image she wants to convey. Since Hsin-Lei works as an independent composer, I proposed a close shot to fill the frame as much as possible. An extra finding during our conversation is that Hsin-Lei is a visual person: through her studies and travelings, she records inspirations by shooting photos. Many of her music pieces were finished with the reference of those image resources and abstract sketches.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><strong>Biography<\\/strong> Since Hsin-Lei only had a press blog before, for content strategy and SEO purpose, a biography statement documenting her styles and accomplishments will help visitors uncover some prospects of her music.<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li><strong>Playlist <\\/strong>Make a list of her selected work, whose length will change by the number of songs. It needs a responsive design so that the site will appear just as good even when the list becomes very long. The order of songs should be adjustable so Hsin-Lei can always choose to display her proudest work on the top.\\r\\n\\t<\\/li>\\r\\n\\t<li>\\r\\n\\t<strong>Awards<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\tCleverly use page spaces to display her awards by using feature articles. If she had released an album, include good reviews and reviewers\' quotes for it.<\\/li><li><strong>Content Management<\\/strong> The building of the portfolio is a continuous commitment and evolve along with her career. So its contents should be manageable via a CMS.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"39\":{\"156\":{\"type\":\"step\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"155\"]}}},\"23\":\"Project Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>I\'ve got a chance to make a portfolio website for Hsin-Lei: a friend of mine, and a talented classical\\/experimental music composer.<\\/p><p>To fully understand Hsin-Lei\'s music before determining the art direction, we kept discussing about her musical pieces and exchanging my design blueprints with her feedbacks. I found her styles were heavily influenced by the European masters of classical music. Grown up and rooted in Chinese culture, most of her songs are also relevant to traditional Chinese literature and philosophies, flavored her work with some unique Asian tastes. Those conversations inspired me of a multimedia website, which represents the essential spirits of her work, using a calm color palette and some stylish photography.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"Hsin-Lei Chen\",\"11\":\"http:\\/\\/hsinlei.com\",\"58\":\"blue\",\"25\":{\"138\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a\\r\\ndesktop feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts. This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"137\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"desktop\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"103\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"136\",\"134\",\"135\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"181\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Interface Design\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci