tent Management<\\/strong> The building of the portfolio is a continuous commitment and evolve along with her career. So its contents should be manageable via a CMS.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"39\":\"\",\"23\":\"Project Analysis\",\"20\":\"<p>I\'ve got a chance to make a portfolio website for Hsin-Lei: a friend of mine, and a talented classical\\/experimental music composer.<\\/p><p>To fully understand Hsin-Lei\'s music before determining the art direction, we kept discussing about her musical pieces and exchanging my design blueprints with her feedbacks. I found her styles were heavily influenced by the European masters of classical music. Grown up and rooted in Chinese culture, most of her songs are also relevant to traditional Chinese literature and philosophies, flavored her work with some unique Asian tastes. Those conversations inspired me of a multimedia website, which represents the essential spirits of her work, using a calm color palette and some stylish photography.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"19\":\"Project Brief\",\"10\":\"Hsin-Lei Chen\",\"11\":\"http:\\/\\/hsinlei.com\",\"58\":\"blue\",\"25\":{\"472\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Ideation\",\"body\":\"<p>For pre-production, I gathered many inspirational references to start designing. The site visual should be unique also precisely describe Hsin-Lei\\u2019s offbeat style. We want to create some documentary archive for only musics rather than any distractions look too promotional.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"471\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"138\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a\\r\\ndesktop feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts. This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"137\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"desktop\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"103\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"This is a feature.\",\"body\":\"<p>This is the feature texts.\\r\\n<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"136\",\"134\",\"135\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"1\"}},\"181\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Interface Design\",\"body\":\"<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat. Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur. Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum.<\\/p>\",\"media\":[\"180\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}},\"171\":{\"type\":\"mediaFeature\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"User Testing Iterations\",\"body\":\"<p>After the first version design, I led individual user tests with 8 users, here is one sample clip. Most tested users like the visual style and the navigation is generally easy to follow. Because of the flat and intuitive striation, almost every user is able to click through the site smoothly.\\r\\n<\\/p><p>There are 3 possible improvements that I think will enhance the overall user experience:<\\/p><ul><li>\\r\\n\\r\\nUsers would like to learn more about the artist from the landing page than her name and photo.<\\/li><li>Google Analytics reported that only 7.7% users (based on 78 users sample) clicked the contact page, and no one used the contact form. Maybe because user could find social media icons and personal contact on the same page.<\\/li><li>\\r\\n\\r\\nThere is high bounce rate between song tracks\' transition, my hypothesis is enhancing the loading effect to better engage users.<\\/li><\\/ul>\",\"media\":[\"172\"],\"layout\":\"full\",\"device\":\"none\",\"allowEnlarge\":\"\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Application\",\"14\":\"Composer\\r\\nHsin-Lei Chen\\r\\nPortfolio\",\"22\":\"<p>A good design fo