e ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo.<\\/p>\",\"images\":[\"215\",\"216\"],\"firstCaption\":\"Site Control\",\"secondCaption\":\"Test\",\"fadeEnabled\":\"1\"}}},\"49\":\"Web Design\",\"14\":\"ACCPI\\r\\nCommunity Website\",\"22\":\"<p>I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan. To coincide with the a series of the campaign, our team was under extreme pressure to move fast. We were tasked to deliver from ideation to high\\u2010fidelity prototype to our technical production partner within 4 weeks, so it requires quick turnarounds. The combination of a fixed deadline, content strategy, usability testing, and usability testing meant I needed to get the experience right in the first two weeks.<\\/p>\",\"21\":\"What I\'ve Learned\",\"43\":[\"327\"],\"17\":\" I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan.\",\"18\":\"\",\"16\":\"ACCPI Community Website\",\"13\":[\"7\"],\"42\":[\"481\"],\"50\":\"https:\\/\\/accpi.org\\/\",\"44\":[\"16\"],\"12\":\"Researches, Wireframes, UX Design & Testing\",\"3\":\" I have taken this project from half-way, and the idea, use flow and even marketing strategy has been changed a lot from our original plan.\",\"9\":[\"photoshop\",\"axure\",\"sketch\"],\"4\":\"2015\"}}', '2015-11-11 05:19:33', '2015-11-11 05:19:33', 'b7cf826c-4812-4b9b-8040-6210e3b3f54b');
