 ('29', '146', 'en_us', 'Design - Wireframes', '<p>Based on the above data and user analysis, I think the key point for the new pricing page should be:\r\n</p><ul>\r\n	<li>Focus on Pricing itself instead of explain un unfamiliar concept for visitors(especially as we are using a new pricing model and drive traffic, there will be more first-time-visitor.)</li>\r\n	<li>Clearly present what we sell to visitors: it is a combo of partially functional mobile app and a web dashboard, so what users finally get will meet their expectation.</li>\r\n	<li>\"Why should I pay if you have a free plan?\" will be the No1 question visitor will ask if he/ she see our pricing page; emphasize the free plan but also compare it with our other plan.</li>\r\n	<li>Target visitors better by supplying related testimonial and Q&As (also valuable for future analysis and improvement.)</li>\r\n</ul>', 'full', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2015-07-26 23:06:42', '2015-08-29 21:43:01', '57373b5b-9443-4f32-a6ec-2e541b152719'),
 ('30', '149', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Design - Wireframes', '<p>Based on the above data and user analysis, I think the key point for the new pricing page should be:</p><ul><li>Focus on Pricing itself instead of explain un unfamiliar concept for visitors(especially as we are using a new pricing model and drive traffic, there will be more first-time-visitor.)</li><li>Clearly present what we sell to visitors: it is a combo of partially functional mobile app and a web dashboard, so what users finally get will meet their expectation.</li><li>\"Why should I pay if you have a free plan?\" will be the No1 question visitor will ask if he/ she see our pricing page; emphasize the free plan but also compare it with our other plan.</li><li>Target visitors better by supplying related testimonial and Q&As (also valuable for future analysis and improvement.)</li></ul>', 'Plan A', 'Plan B', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '1', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2015-07-26 23:34:33', '2015-08-29 21:43:01', '3dec9261-2240-48a4-8593-e1b6b2d933cc'),
