 ('33', '171', 'en_us', 'User Testing Iterations', '<p>After the first version design, I led individual user tests with 8 users, here is one sample clip. Most tested users like the visual style and the navigation is generally easy to follow. Because of the flat and intuitive striation, almost every user is able to click through the site smoothly.\r\n</p><p>There are 3 possible improvements that I think will enhance the overall user experience:</p><ul><li>\r\n\r\nUsers would like to learn more about the artist from the landing page than her name and photo.</li><li>Google Analytics reported that only 7.7% users (based on 78 users sample) clicked the contact page, and no one used the contact form. Maybe because user could find social media icons and personal contact on the same page.</li><li>\r\n\r\nThere is high bounce rate between song tracks\' transition, my hypothesis is enhancing the loading effect to better engage users.</li></ul>', 'full', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2015-08-20 02:53:23', '2015-11-11 05:00:51', '8660012a-808c-44a9-8e8f-e3f852b6f8ea'),
 ('34', '179', 'en_us', 'Conversation Design', '<p>To make the Fengshui 3D experience more engaging, introducing characters into this project\r\nwas an innovative approach. The characters have a welcome page when users enter rooms,\r\na thank you page when users finished all the tasks in the rooms, and during the exploring\r\nprocess, the characters are on the bottom righthand corner of the screen and will occasionally\r\nping the visitors some hints. Users can click the characters and ask for those clues as well.</p>', 'full', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'none', '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, NULL, '2015-08-23 22:01:02', '2015-10-17 22:01:20', '01f17123-53fa-4a3f-bbeb-bdb4845b785c'),
