 ('6', 'field', '20', 'en_us', ' the real time experience is an interactive educational project that introduces daily feng shui tips to college students office workers and anyone who wants to learn how feng shui can enhance their lives this project uses web gl technology that runs on any computer with an up to date modern browser the user flow is a simple four step process listen observe find and solve this is how feng shui masters help people figure out their problems it is an engaging practice because users become actively involved in the whole problem solving experience my goal for this project is to present the principles and rules of feng shui philosophy as well as its applications in modern interior design and to interpret feng shui through creative interactive experience i wish that by introducing feng shui to new western audience they can benefit from learning feng shui theories and improve their living environment '),
 ('6', 'field', '21', 'en_us', ' what i ve learned '),
 ('6', 'field', '22', 'en_us', ' during my user testing process i found that most people skip over intro tours as quickly as possible ant those that didn t rarely remember what they were supposed to learn because they haven t seen the interface yet so they don t have any sense of where and how the tips they re learning will apply here comes the just in time education concept i ve tried different methods to solve this problem for example by overlaying the tuts on top of the actual interface design but even so people lack the experience to know ehich actions will be useful to them and when besides over time they ve likely to forget some of the functions since they didn t take that action immediately after they ve learnt so instead of trying to teach everything up front and all at once teach in the moment when specific information is actually useful in my case i tried to provide only the nessasary tips for visitors for instance if a user start exploring the 3d scence by click i will suggest him scroll mouse wheel vice versa besides last but not least the how to instruction is always on the left corner of the page make it easier for visitors to check out anytime the trick to getting just in time education right is revealing useful information when people actually need it not when they don t '),
